The paper deals with the design of auctions, which is a topic in game theory and mechanism design, falling under the category of cs.GT (Game Theory and Decision Science). The use of deep learning in the design process suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The evaluation of the designed auctions involves optimization and efficiency, which are topics in computer science (cs.DS). Finally, the paper deals with economic mechanisms, which falls under the category of cs.EC (Economics and Computation).
